<div
    class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[560px] lg:mr-0 scroll-mt-24 self-end overflow-hidden rounded-4xl
    border border-white/80 bg-white/82 p-8 text-[#19364a]
    shadow-[0_24px_80px_-48px_rgba(0,0,0,0.75)] backdrop-blur sm:p-5
    lg:mb-8"
>
    <div class="mb-4">
        <p class="mt-2 top-badge-neutral">Asistente Inteligente</p>

        <p class="text-sm leading-7 py-3 text-slate-600 md:text-lg">
            Vera te ayuda a identificar qué procesos de tu negocio podrían
            organizarse, mejorarse o automatizarse.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 p-2 w-full">
        <div class="space-y-2">
            <h3
                class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2"
            >
                <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-500
                        drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(34,211,238,0.8)]"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="currentColor"
                >
                    <path
                        d="M12 0C12 6.627 17.373 12 24 12C17.373 12 12 17.373 12 24C12 17.373 6.627 12 0 12C6.627 12 12 6.627 12 0Z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>
                <span
                    class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-br
                        from-teal-400 via-primary to-base-content/80"
                >
                    Probá Vera gratis
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-slate-500">
                Contanos un problema de tu equipo.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative group">
            <!-- Glow effect (Neon) -->
            <div
                class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500
                to-purple-500 rounded-2xl blur opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-60
                transition duration-500"
            >
            </div>

            <!-- Input container -->
            <div
                class="relative flex flex-col bg-base-100 backdrop-blur-xl
                rounded-2xl border border-cyan-900/50 shadow-inner p-4 transition-all"
            >
                <textarea
                    class="w-full resize-none border-0 bg-transparent text-sm
                    md:text-base text-gray-500 placeholder-gray-500 focus:ring-0
                    outline-none"
                    rows="3"
                    >Recibimos muchos WhatsApp y nadie sabe quién respondió...</textarea
                >

                <!-- Button -->
                <div
                    class="mt-4 flex justify-end border-t border-cyan-900/30 pt-3"
                >
                    <a
                        href="#vera"
                        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary
                             to-base-content px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(6,182,212,0.4)] hover:shadow-[0_0_25px_rgba(6,182,212,0.6)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-cyan-400 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-[#0f2434] active:scale-95"
                    >
                        Hablar con Vera
                        <svg
                            class="h-4 w-4"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="2.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
